songplayer

Class EndOfSongEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • songplayer.EndOfSongEvent

  • public class EndOfSongEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    An instance of this class is needed to create an EndOfSongListener to pass as an argument to the listener. This provides the programmer with the ability to get the name of the audio file, the date and the time when the song is done.
    Author:
    mercer
